title: Malcom Distributors 2.5 mm Female to 3.5 mm Male 3 Rings Jack Stereo Adapter On/Off Enabled
description:
Converts your 2.5mm stereo headset to a 3.5mm jack stereo headset. If your 2.5mm headset is on/off enabled so will the jack converted ones.This adapter will work with the following phones:iPhone first generation, 3G, 3GS
